thread.title_full: Transmembrane oligomeric intermediates of pore forming toxin Cytolysin A determine leakage kinetics

posts.author: Ayush Agrawal
posts.title: Transmembrane oligomeric intermediates of pore forming toxin Cytolysin A determine leakage kinetics
posts.text: a Department of Chemical Engineering, Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore-560012, India E-mail: b Department of Chemical Engineering, Indian Institute of Technology, Hyderabad-502205, India c Centre for Biosystems Science and Engineering, Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore-560012, India Abstract Calcein leakage experiments for the α pore forming toxin Cytolysin A (ClyA) are carried out using a suspension of small unilamellar vesicles made up of 1,2-dipalmitoyl- sn -glycero-3-phosphocholine (DPPC) and cholesterol. Combining the oligomerization kinetics with a Poisson process to describe the inherent stochasticity underlying pore formation, we screen possible oligomerization pathways by comparing model predictions with calcein leakage data for ClyA. Excellent agreement with the leakage data was obtained for a reversible sequential oligomerization mechanism upon inclusion of leakage from membrane inserted partially oligomerized intermediates or ‘arcs’. In contrast, the non-sequential mechanisms were unable to predict the calcein leakage data. Reversibility in the oligomerization mechanism maintains a constant supply of protomers resulting in a broad distribution of oligomers at steady state. Additionally, the time scale for the conformational change from the water soluble monomer to the membrane bound protomer was found to be similar or larger than the time scale for oligomerization. The dominant contribution to leakage was found to occur from the smaller arcs, consistent with the low protein to lipid ratios used in the experiment. Our kinetic model is able to capture both the fast and slow time constants typically observed in calcein leakage experiments. A key inference is that arcs play a critical role in the leakage kinetics of ClyA, with the fast leakage time scale arising from the smaller oligomerized intermediates and the longer time scale arising from the slowly forming higher order oligomers.

posts.title: ZephVR会在你的脸上吹气 让VR更加真实_智能_环球网
posts.text:
根据外媒Digital Trends的报道，ZephVR可能会在你脸上吹气，它是Oculus Rift、HTC Vive和PlaystationVR等虚拟现实头戴设备的配件，可以让用户感觉到自己的动作。 
据了解，这款ZephVR配件可以附在目前的虚拟现实头戴设备上，利用机器学习技术在你的脸上吹气，模拟真实的风和运动，让用户获得更加真实的体验。 
虚拟现实最大的困难之一是，它看起来真实，但实际上并没有多少感觉。你可能会觉得自己在那里，但除了在控制器中通过马达进行一些触觉反馈之外，在游戏和体验中并没有触摸感应。当你在空中飞行或在地面上奔跑时，这一点可能最为明显，因为你没有感觉到你脸上的空气流动。 
这就是ZephVR配件的设计初衷。它看起来有点像Vive的冷却系统，但ZephVR的设计不仅仅是降温，它应该能让你感受到风在你脸上划过的感觉。 
ZephVR的工作原理是让用户在游戏中听到“风”的声音，在游戏中，“风”是显而易见的，并伴随着听到的提示音。开发者们声称他们已经将游戏内音频进行了分类，然后使用机器学习来挑选唯一的标识符。 
目前，这款ZephVR配件正在众筹平台Kickstarter上筹集资金，其众筹价格为50美元。这款产品可以为 Oculus Rift用户提供15英尺的mini-USB数据线。如果一切顺利的话，这款产品预计将于明年5月份开始正式出货，不过与所有Kickstarter众筹项目一样，这一计划并不是一成不变的。 相关新闻

posts.author: Mark Townsend
posts.title: Tiger: We need to talk about the golf ball
posts.text:
Tiger: We need to talk about the golf ball November 7, 2017 Golf News 
In this week's Talking Point we look at Tiger Woods' podcast debut as he finally joins in the debate on the distance the modern ball travels 
“I can’t believe how far I’m hitting the golf ball. I’m back to hitting it my full numbers, and not really trying to do that.” 
The first part of this could be any of us sat in the clubhouse after a recent lesson had helped crank our swing speed up to 98mph, the second part would just be a bit weird and might well, and quite rightly, see you excluded you from next week’s fourball. 
But these are the words of Tiger Woods last week and, rather than being a humble brag, instead he’s been talking about the modern golf ball. And when Tiger talks, we all sit up and listen. 
Jack Nicklaus has been one of the more vocal exponents of ‘rolling the ball back’, the Golden Bear would favour something like a 10 per cent reduction in the distance that the ball travels. 
Last year at the Masters he had these options on the possible changes to the world-famous par-5 13th at Augusta. 
You could make it a par 4, not going to happen. 
You could buy some additional property from Augusta Country Club, which is the plan. 
You could move the green back 30 yards or you could reroute the stream and put some more trees in. 
Or, as Jack laughingly added: “The simplest solution is change the frigging golf ball. The golf ball goes so far, Augusta National is about the only golf course in the world that financially can afford to make the changes that they have to make to keep up with the golf ball. I don’t think anybody else could ever do it.” 
Tiger, making his podcast debut with UConn women’s basketball coach Geno Auriemma (me neither), said that he could see an 8,000-yard course – so imagine your home course and then adding maybe 1,500 yards – being around the corner in order to stage a professional tournament. 
“With the game progressing as it is, I think the 8,000-yard golf course is not too far away,” he said. “That’s pretty scary – we don’t have enough property to start designing these types of golf courses, and it just makes it so much more complicated. We need to do something about the golf ball. I just think [the ball] is going too far. 
“The USGA is already looking at it . They’re doing some research on what would the world look like if you rolled [the ball] back 10, 15 and 20 per cent. You don’t want to [take away] amateurs’ [ability] to hit the ball further and straighter. But with the tour pros, you might want to roll the ball back.” 
Sound familiar? 
Jack’s been saying it for years, now Tiger is well on board as is anyone with half a brain. 
So, when can we expect all this to happen? 
In truth, no time soon. Like we said Jack’s been banging this drum for some time and nothing’s changed so any backing down by the governing bodies might make them look a bit silly. Why now? Tennis brought in a new ball in 2002 so why is golf so late to the party? 
Think of the huge bundles of money involved to keep the ball manufacturers happy. 
At best someone might trial a tournament with rolled back ball which brings back in all the incredible courses that have become outdated and lost to tournament play in the past few years, or a variety of exhibitions. 
Think of all the amazing recovery shots we might get to witness with the ball now being able to be manufactured around the course, think of a tournament where 20 under isn’t the winning total. It’s quite exciting isn’t it? 
Tiger said he and his peers have spoken with the tour’s law makers about how a roll back might work. 
“Do we have it at the PGA Tour level? Do we have it at the Web.com level? Do we have it on all mini tours? So there’s that debate as well. I don’t see it happening in the near future but at least there are talks about it now.” 
As for Tiger getting back to hitting it full pelt he also had this to say which, to even someone as cynical as me, it does begin to get the mind whirring with the ‘ what if he could contend again ’ just a little. 
“I didn’t realise how much I had dropped off because of the pain in my back and from me going at it and hitting it normal just because I just lived it from day to day and I really couldn’t tell the difference. But now I can tell the difference and my posture is so much better over the golf ball.” 
He’s back in action at the Hero Challenge on November 30. Read more..

posts.text:
Американското воздухопловство не го пријавило убиецот од Тексас како осуден криминалец Американското воздухопловство не го пријавило убиецот од Тексас како осуден криминалец watch_later 07. ноември 2017. @ 09:48   69   2 мин. 
Американските воздухопловни сили признаа дека на Федерелното биро за истраги (FBI) не му го пријавиле податокот дека Девин Патрик Кели, кој во нападот во сојузната држава Тексас уби 26 и рани 20 лица, порано бил осуден за семејно насилство, што би ја спречило можноста легално да набави огнено оружје. 
„Според првите податоци, осудата против Кели за семејно насилство не е внесена во регистерот“, изјави портпарлката на американското воздухопловство Ен Стефанек, додавајќи дека е покрената истрага за да се утврди дали има уште пресуди коишто не се впишани во регистерот. 
Според уредбата на американското министерство за добрана, персоналот на Пентагон мора да го извести FBI за секоја пресуда на воениот суд за да биде впишана во регистарот. 
Пред пет години воениот суд го осудил Кели поради напад врз сопругата и посинокот, но од Американските воздухопловни сили соопштија дека тоа не е пријавено во Националната база со податоци за сторителите на злостроства коишто се под надзор на FBI. Кели бил осуден на 12 месеци затвор и ослободен во 2014 година, и без почести отпуштен од војската. 
Според американскиот федерален закон, врз основа на оваа пресуда тој немал право да купи ниту да поседува оружје, појасни портпаролката Стефанек. 
Американските воздухопловни сили објавиле во 2013 година документ во кој подробно се наведени причини за пресудата против Девин Патрик Кели: пригласен е виновен бидејќи неколкупати во периодот од јуни 2011 до април 2012 година ја претепал сопругата, ја удирал со нозе и се обидел да ја задави. Покрај тоа, осуден е и за тоа што го тепал посинокот, со сила којашто можела да предизвика смрт или тешки повреди. 
И во двата случаи ја признал вината, но не ја признал вината дека двапата, во јануари и април 2012 година, им се заканувал на сопругата и посинокот со оружје. 
Девин Патрик Кели се убил по обидот да побегне од местотпо на масакрот. Бил облечен во црно и носел зашттен непробоен елек и полуавтоматска пушка кога влегол во Првата баптистичка црква во Сандерленд Спрингс, место со околу 400 жители. Во нападот уби 26 луѓе, меѓу кои и 18-месечно бебе, а рани уште 20 лици, а меѓу кои и момче од пет години, а повеќемина се уште во критична состојба.

posts.title: Cardinal Health CEO to Step Down -- WSJ
posts.text:
Move comes as lower generics prices squeeze profits, and company faces suits over opioids
By Allison Prang
This article is being republished as part of our daily reproduction of WSJ.com articles that also appeared in the U.S. print edition of The Wall Street Journal (November 7, 2017).
Cardinal Health Inc. said Monday that Chief Executive George Barrett will step down in January after more than eight years in the post, as pricing pressure for generic drugs has weighed on the company in recent months.
Mr. Barrett, 62 years old, will remain in his role as executive chairman until the company's shareholder meeting in November 2018. Lead independent director Gregory Kenny will then become nonexecutive chairman, the company said.
Chief Financial Officer Mike Kaufmann, 54 years old, will become the chief executive of the pharmaceutical and medical-supplies distributor on Jan. 1.
Cardinal Health also announced that Jorge Gomez, CFO of Cardinal Health's medical division, will be taking over as finance chief of the entire company.
Cardinal Health, similar to other pharmaceutical wholesalers and manufacturers, has been hurt by lower generic-drug prices, which the company said in April won't improve until the middle of 2018.
On Monday, the company said first-quarter profits in its pharmaceutical division fell 13% compared with last year, partly due to the decline in generic drug prices.
Overall profit fell 63% from a year ago to $115 million, as higher expenses also weighed on the firm. On an adjusted basis, earnings fell 13% to $346 million. Adjusted earnings per share were $1.09, beating analysts' estimates of $1.
Revenue rose 2% to $32.6 billion. Shares fell 1.7% to $60.36 in Monday trading.
Cardinal Health recently completed its $6.1 billion purchase of Medtronic PLC's patient-recovery business to bolster its portfolio of medical products. Earlier this year the company said it would explore a sale of its China distribution operations.
Cardinal Health is also facing lawsuits filed by New Mexico and dozens of counties nationwide, alleging the company contributed to widespread addiction to opioid painkillers by failing to control distribution of the drugs. In its 2017 annual report, the company said it was "vigorously defending" itself against those suits, which in part allege companies violated controlled-substance laws.
Cardinal Health announced Mr. Barrett's planned departure two days before its shareholder meeting. Last month, the International Brotherhood of Teamsters sent a letter to shareholders saying the structure of Cardinal Health's board was "inadequate" to respond to its "decadelong role in fueling the opioid crisis." The Teamsters, whose funds own over $27 million of shares of Cardinal Health, asked shareholders to vote to remove Mr. Barrett as chairman.
Ken Hall, the Teamsters' general secretary-treasurer, said Monday in a statement that the company's recent moves shows the union's message is being received. The union also wants an independent board committee to study Cardinal Health business practices and compliance programs related to opioids.
Cardinal Health said in an emailed statement that "the separation of chairman and CEO was not in response to any group."
"The board always takes into account a wide range of factors, including the current practices of others, as well as the views of shareholders," the company said. "This was a natural time to move forward with our plan."
The Teamsters' message to Cardinal Health shareholders was their most recent move against a medical company related to opioids. The labor group also prodded shareholders of McKesson Corp. to appoint an independent chairman instead of McKesson CEO John Hammergren and to vote down a proposal regarding his compensation. Shareholders ended up opposing the pay proposal in July.
McKesson said after the vote that it takes "feedback seriously and will carefully consider the input received."

Νέο κτίριο θα αποκτήσει η κυπριακή Βουλή Δημοσιεύθηκε: 07 Νοεμβρίου 2017, 10:57 ΒΟΥΛΗ 
Νέο σύγχρονο , λειτουργικό και αξιοπρεπές κτίριο για τις ανάγκες της επιθυμεί η κυπριακή Βουλή , ενώ αναμένεται πως θα είναι έτοιμο τ ο 2023. 
Συγκεκριμένα, σύμφωνα με τη γενική διευθύντρια της Βουλής, Βασιλική Αναστασιάδου, το κόστος της ανέγερσης του νέου κτιρίου είναι 72 εκατομμύρια ευρώ και στο σύνολό του αναμένεται να είναι έτοιμο έως το 2023. 
«Μετά την αξιολόγηση των προσφερόμενων λύσεων έχουμε καταλήξει στην επιλογή της ανέγερσης νέου κτιρίου της Βουλής στον χώρο που απαλλοτριώθηκε παλαιότερα» ανέφερε η κ. Αναστασιάδου, υπενθυμίζοντας πως το 1994 είχε διεξαχθεί αρχιτεκτονικός διαγωνισμός, στο οποίο το πρώτο βραβείο είχε δοθεί στην ομάδα μελέτης του αρχιτεκτονικού γραφείου Κυθρεώτης και Συνεργάτες. Τα σχέδια εκείνα είχαν αναθεωρηθεί το 2009, όταν επίκειτο η ανάληψη της προεδρίας της ΕΕ από την Κύπρο, ωστόσο ούτε σε εκείνη τη φάση προχώρησε το έργο. 
Όπως σημείωσε η κ. Αναστασιάδου, το 2009 το προϋπολογισθέν κόστος ανερχόταν σε 100 εκατομμύρια ευρώ, όπως μεταδίδει το ΑΜΠΕ, πλην όπως η ίδια τόνισε έγιναν προσαρμογές τέτοιες, που να κατεβάζουν το κόστος στα 72 εκατομμύρια. 
Σε ό,τι αφορά το υφιστάμενο κτίριο, είπε πως θα αξιοποιηθεί κατάλληλα ως παλαιό κτίριο, με διάφορες χρήσεις.   ΔΙΕΘΝΗ ΣΧΟΛΙΑΣΤΕ ΤΟ ΆΡΘΡΟ

Villa i Karlstad står i brand – helt övertänd Publicerad 
En villa står i brand i Karlstad kommun. 
Räddningstjänst och ambulans har larmats till platsen, enligt SOS Alarm. 
– Byggnaden är helt övertänd och kommer nog brinna ner, säger Hans Berged, räddningschef i beredskap vid Räddningstjänsten Karlstadsregionen. 
Larmet om branden kom vid klockan 09.30 på tisdagsmorgonen.

– Det fanns inget att göra när vi kom fram till villan, säger räddningschefen Hans Berged. 
Enligt honom hade personen som bodde tagit sig ut på egen hand. 
Inga personer har skadats i samband med branden. Övervakar branden 
Räddningstjänsten kommer nu låta villan brinna ner. Det finns inga byggnader i närheten som riskerar att påverkas av branden, enligt Hans Berged.

  Pulse para ampliar Toquero en el día de su debut con el Zaragoza. 
Gaizka Toquero se ha convertido en uno de los pesos pesados del vestuario del Real Zaragoza desde su llegada este pasado verano a La Romareda. El exdelantero del Athletic Club , autor de tres goles con la camiseta del conjunto maño esta temporada, no puso paños calientes a la dolorosa derrota (3-1) encajada por su equipo en el derbi ante la SD Huesca en El Alcoraz. El de Ariznabarra se mostró contundente como portavoz del sentir de los jugadores y del zaragocismo tras lo visto en el terreno de juego. 
"Hemos hecho el peor partido de la temporada y nos han superado en todos los aspectos. No hemos estado a la altura de este escudo, de la afición y de la gente que ha venido a pasar frío para animarnos. Sólo queda cada uno mirarnos a nosotros mismos y ver lo que queremos hacer este año. Estamos a tiempo, todavía queda mucha Liga por delante, pero esto no puede volver a pasar. Así no vamos a a ningún lado. Hemos dado vergüenza", lanzó en caliente el delantero gasteiztarra en GOL TV . 
El baño histórico del Huesca al Zaragoza encendió a Toquero que continuó con su contundente ejercicio de autocrítica: "Hemos venido aquí muy relajaditos y creo que un tortazo como estos nos viene bien. Da igual a quien saque el míster hoy, hemos estado todos mal y aunque Borja hubiera marcado la que ha tenido, nos hubieran metido otros tres igual porque no hemos estado a la altura y ellos sí", concluía el exleón. 
El Zaragoza de Natxo González sigue en caída libre y está ya a tres puntos del descenso. El Huesca de Rubi, por contra, es segundo, empatado a puntos con el líder. ¡Atención a la rajada de Toquero después de perder el derbi aragonés! #LosLunesAlGol pic.twitter.com/mlGb8xXRol

posts.text:
[베이징= 이데일리 김인경 특파원] 중국 증시가 도널드 트럼프 미국 대통령의 방중을 앞두고 이틀 연속 상승세로 마감했다.
7일 상하이종합지수는 전 거래일보다 0.75% 오른 3413.57로 거래를 마쳤다. 선전성분지수는 1만1467.97로 전 거래일보다 0.83% 올랐다.
인터넷 보안업체인 치후360의 우회상장 잇에 관련 테마주들이 상승세를 이끌었다. 지난 3일 A주에 상장돼 있는 장난자제 엘리베이터는 거래를 중단한 후 상장사 주주가 치후360을 이끄는 저우훙웨이 회장이 된다고 발표한 바 있다. 지난해 뉴욕증시에서 상장폐지된 치후360이 상하이증시에서 우회상장된다는 소식에 장난자제 등 관련 종목이 상한가로 치솟았다.
트럼프 대통령의 방중에 대한 기대도 증시의 강세를 이끌었다. 트럼프 대통령은 8일부터 10일까지 베이징을 방문해 시진핑 중국 주석을 만날 예정이다. 이 자리에서 두 정상은 에너지, 제조 분야 등을 포함한 다양한 분야에서 수많은 양해각서를 체결할 것으로 기대된다.
한편 8일엔 중국의 수출입 지표와 무역수지가 발표된다. 위안화 기준으로 중국의 9월 수출은 작년 같은 기간보다 9.0%, 수입은 19.5% 증가했다. 무역흑자는 1930억위안(약 33조2270억원)으로 전년 동기보다 28% 줄어든 바 있다.

【环球网综合报道】据 英国 《每日邮报》11月6日报道，近日，53岁的 奥地利 艺术家 马里 奥•昂格尔（Mario Unger）费尽心思处理了一些老照片，用PS对它们进行修复并添加色彩，以独特的视角为人们展现了一段段不为所知的历史。 
马里奥还原的老照片都拍摄于19世纪中末期和20世纪初期，有的甚至超过了150年之久。这些照片中，有的恰好记录下了 美国 历史上具有重要意义的时刻，如美国内战时期，总统林肯与联邦军将领 乔治 •布林顿• 麦克 莱伦（George B McClellan）在帐篷内会面；有的拍摄下了宾夕法尼亚骑兵团中的军官们。 
此外，有一张照片拍摄于1865年，画面中一群来自中西部美国原住民部落的庞卡 印第安人 （Ponca Indians）手持刀斧坐在一起。还有的是美国第15任总统 詹姆斯 •布坎南（James Buchanan）的单人照和许多普通人的生活照。 
这些被还原后的照片颜色鲜活、形象生动，活灵活现地为人们展现了弥足珍贵的历史记忆。（实习编译：刘慧婷 审稿：朱盈库） 本网登载图片出于更直观传递信息之目的，并不代表本网赞同其观点和对其真实性负责，谢绝转载。如该图片涉及任何第三方合法权利，请及时与lawyer@huanqiu.com联系。 本图集所有图片已播放完毕

posts.text:
Son Güncelleme: 07.11.2017 - 11:59 
Allianz Global Corporate & Specialty (AGCS), uluslararası nakit transferi de dahil olmak üzere blockhain çözümünü başarıyla denediğini duyurdu. AGCS yan kuruluşu olan Allianz Risk Transfer AG (ART), muhasebe firması EY ile işbirliği yaparak, blok zinciri prototip çözümü başarıyla yaratmak için dijital ajans Ginetta'yla işbirliği yaptı. ART ayrıca, Allianz'ın blok zincir prototipiyle ilgili ödeme işlem hizmetleri sağlayan Citi Hazine ve Ticaret Çözümleri ile de bir araya geldi. AGCS'e göre, sonuçlar, blok zincir teknolojisinin uluslararası kurumsal sigorta işlemlerinin etkinliğini artırabileceğini kanıtladı. 
Blocklaın çerçevesi Hyperledger Fabric 1.0 üzerine kurulmuş olan prototip, ABD, Çin ve İsviçre'deki yerel iştiraklerle birlikte captive sigortası için iki tür sağlık sigortası (mesleki tazminat ve mülkiyet) içeriyor. Allianz'a göre, sigortayı satın almak yerine sigortalanan çok uluslu kuruluşlar tarafından kurulan avukatlık sigortası programları ticari sigortanın en karmaşık yönü olarak kabul edilmekte.
